Project Zomboid Mods Repository

This branch is the showcase/root branch for my Project Zomboid mod projects.

Projects:
- Quick Restart
- Competitive Play Framework

Branch layout:
- PZ-Hub: showcase/root branch
- QuickRestart: project overview branch
- QR-Main: Quick Restart stable branch
- QR-Dev: Quick Restart development branch
- CPF: project overview branch
- CPF-Main: Competitive Play Framework stable branch
- CPF-Dev: Competitive Play Framework development branch

This branch intentionally stays lightweight and acts as a starting point for the
project-specific branches.
